text: Arif Moinuddin is a Bangladesh Nationalist Party politician and the former Member of Parliament of Chittagong-9. ==Career== Moinuddin was elected to parliament from Chittagong-9 as a Bangladesh Nationalist Party candidate in 1979. ==References== Category:Bangladesh Nationalist Party politicians Category:Living people Category:2nd Jatiya Sangsad members Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Arif Moinuddin
